thread.title_full: Initial Hygiene IE reviewed by Louise Kenny

author: Louise Kenny
title: Louise Kenny
text: Experience with dealing with Initial Hygiene has been very positive to date (March 2017). My main contact is a lady by the name of Antoinette Walsh. She has made my dealings with the company a very positive experience and all queries are dealt with professionally and efficiently.
